work.position: Workday Custom Report and Prism Analytics Developer
highlights: Led the development of a multi-source data pipeline integrating Epic EMR, Kronos, Axiom, and Workday data.
Engineered data pipelines to unify systems, improving reporting accuracy.
Managed migration of 12 million rows of legacy data into Workday Prism Analytics.
Developed over 100 advanced reports across payroll, HCM, and recruiting.
Created detailed payroll reports at cost center and employee levels.
Generated quarterly job application and termination reports for Vizient reporting.
Built a dashboard tracking employee turnover trends and attrition rates.
Designed metrics for continuous service and terminations within specific timeframes.
Executed deployment of Workday HCM data reporting for Highland Hospital.
Partnered with Huron consultants to ensure data consistency during the transition.
Deployed W-2 and W-2C data extraction for Highland Hospital workers.
Customized BIRT paycheck layout for over 4000 workers using Workday Studio.
Designed BIRT supplier payment checks to bank specifications.
Developed a financial dashboard to monitor $64 million in grant funding.
Devised an on-demand solution for database migration using SQL and hash algorithms.
Upgraded and maintained SSIS ETL workflows.
Managed SQL queries for the Facets insurance claim submission application.
Encouraged process improvements leading to increased productivity.
Prevented loss of $1.6 million in unused state aid through strategic data analysis.
Processed daily billing for the HHUNY network using SSIS workflows.
Engineered a data pipeline for $35 million in budget data.
Developed Tableau dashboards with daily refresh.
Built a GUI application using Microsoft Access and SQL Server for the 'Gap In Care' initiative.
Analyzed 188,000 rows of travel data from 19,000 household surveys using a custom Java application.

honors: Brockport Math and Computer Science Scholarship for three consecutive semesters
